public interface StdSequence<T>

Basic interface of associative container.

作成者:
hiroaki.kubota@mail.rakuten.co.jp

メソッドの概要
 StdIterator<T> begin()
           Find lowest data in this container.
 void erase(StdIterator<T> it)
           Remove data from this container.
 StdIterator<T> last()
           Find highest data in this container.
 

メソッドの詳細

begin

StdIterator<T> begin()
 Find lowest data in this container.

戻り値:
Returns iterator of pointing the first data or end of container(when this container is empty).

last

StdIterator<T> last()
 Find highest data in this container.

戻り値:
Returns iterator of pointing the last data or end of container(when this container is empty).

erase

void erase(StdIterator<T> it)
 Remove data from this container.

パラメータ:
it - Iterator of pointing removing data.
